---
import BaseLayout from "../../../layouts/BaseLayout.astro";
---
<BaseLayout lang="en" current="hvac" title="HVAC" description="Heating, ventilation and air conditioning. Our facilities allow you to improve hygiene conditions in your building by reducing CO2 levels in the air, but also p">
  <section class="section">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="page-content">
        <div class="breadcrumb"><a href="/en/">Home</a> <span>/</span> <a href="/en/hvac/">HVAC</a></div>
        <div style="margin: -2rem -2rem 2rem -2rem; height: 220px; background: url('/images/hvac.jpg') center/cover no-repeat; border-radius: 0 0 var(--radius-lg) var(--radius-lg);"></div>
        <h1>HVAC</h1>
        <p>Heating, ventilation and air conditioning. Our facilities allow you to improve hygiene conditions in your building by reducing CO2 levels in the air, but also pollutants, different particles and odors. The HVAC system we master with care and safety is also used in the management of room temperature and humidity ( atmospheric humidity ) . This ultimately allows us to control the pressure ( overpressure ) to our customers in the food .</p>

<p><a href="/en/contact">Contact us</a> without further ado, we offer a suitable solution with fast delivery and unbeatable prices!</p>

      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
  <section class="section section-gray">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="section-title">
        <h2>Our HVAC services</h2>
      </div>
      <div class="grid-3">
          <div class="card">
            <h3><a href="/en/hvac/troubleshooting/">HVAC Troubleshooting</a></h3>
            <p>AC troubleshooting. Fast service.</p>
            <a href="/en/hvac/troubleshooting/" style="color:var(--primary);font-weight:600;font-size:0.9rem">→ Request a free quote</a>
          </div>
          <div class="card">
            <h3><a href="/en/hvac/installation/">HVAC Installation</a></h3>
            <p>HVAC, ventilation, extraction.</p>
            <a href="/en/hvac/installation/" style="color:var(--primary);font-weight:600;font-size:0.9rem">→ Request a free quote</a>
          </div>
          <div class="card">
            <h3><a href="/en/hvac/repair/">HVAC Repair</a></h3>
            <p>HVAC repair all brands.</p>
            <a href="/en/hvac/repair/" style="color:var(--primary);font-weight:600;font-size:0.9rem">→ Request a free quote</a>
          </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
  <section class="section" style="text-align:center">
    <div class="container">
      <a href="/en/contact" class="btn btn-accent" style="font-size:1.1rem;padding:1rem 2.5rem">Request a free quote →</a>
    </div>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>
